Chairman cuts Interform stake by 2 . 5 pct . Interform Ceramics Technologies Ltd said on Tuesday that its chairman Ngan Man Po had sold 18 million shares , or 2 . 53 percent of the company issued share capital , on September 27 . Ngan ' s Great Chance Holdings Ltd held 62 . 49 percent of the ceramics production lines supplier as in January 1996 . It gave no further details . Interform shares ended one cent down at HK $ 0 . 64 per share on Tuesday on volume of 5 . 05 million shares . - - Hong Kong Newsroom ( 852 ) 2843 6370 
